Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:34.14,IN-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3}I’ll be always on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:37.52,IN-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,480)\blur3}Forever…
